Package StyleSheets

Class UnitManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • StyleSheets.UnitManager
  • public abstract class UnitManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Helping class to control and simplify sizing. Can be useful with number manipulation as each methods take an integer value used to determine the size. Every method in this class is static and returns a string that can be used with properties.
